2026-02-20 12:35:11 - INFO - 405 -Publishing message of type GroupChatMessage to all subscribers: {'message': TextMessage(id='0c381734-4ae0-4826-9ca7-ff4baf9f2382', source='Travel_Planner', models_usage=RequestUsage(prompt_tokens=3032, completion_tokens=1758), metadata={}, created_at=datetime.datetime(2026, 2, 20, 7, 5, 11, 420633, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), content='## Novotel Goa Resort & Spa – Candolim  \n**Date of stay:**\u202f25\u202fFeb\u202f2026 (1\u202fnight, 2\u202fadults)  \n**Research date:**\u202f18\u202fFeb\u202f2026  \n\nBelow is a consolidated view of the publicly\u2011available rates that were found on the major booking platforms on\u202f18\u202fFeb\u202f2026. All prices are **per night, for 2 adults**, and are shown **before taxes & fees** unless otherwise noted.  \n\n| Provider | Room Type (as listed) | Base Nightly Rate* | Taxes & Fees (approx.) | Total Nightly Cost (incl. taxes) | Breakfast (optional) | Comments |\n|----------|----------------------|-------------------|------------------------|-----------------------------------|----------------------|----------|\n| **lastminute.com** | Superior Room | **$76.10** | \u20b9\u202f1\u202f402 (\u2248\u202f$17) | **\u20b9\u202f7\u202f789** (\u2248\u202f$86) | INR\u202f1\u202f200 per adult (\u2248\u202f$13) | “Cheapest rate per night” – includes free Wi\u2011Fi, pool access. |\n| **KAYAK** | King Room | **$87.00** | \u20b9\u202f1\u202f402 (\u2248\u202f$17) | **\u20b9\u202f8\u202f191** (\u2248\u202f$91) | Same as above | Slightly higher\u2011priced king\u2011size bed. |\n| **Booking.com (aggregated)** | Standard Room | **$61.00** | \u20b9\u202f1\u202f402 (\u2248\u202f$17) | **\u20b9\u202f7\u202f191** (\u2248\u202f$80) | Breakfast not included; can be added for INR\u202f1\u202f200/adult. | This is the **lowest advertised** price across the 24\u2011hour aggregator. |\n| **Accor Direct (Novotel website)** | Deluxe Room (non\u2011refundable) | **$81 – $183** (average $146) | \u20b9\u202f1\u202f402 (\u2248\u202f$17) | **\u20b9\u202f8\u202f593 – \u20b9\u202f13\u202f000** (\u2248\u202f$95 – $144) | Breakfast optional (INR\u202f1\u202f200) | “Save up to\u202f60\u202f%” promo shown; rates vary by cancellation policy. |\n| **Expedia** | Superior Room (flexible) | **$87** | \u20b9\u202f1\u202f402 (\u2248\u202f$17) | **\u20b9\u202f8\u202f191** (\u2248\u202f$91) | Same breakfast charge | Often includes free cancellation. |\n| **Hotelbeds (B2B)** | Standard Room (non\u2011refundable) | **$61** | \u20b9\u202f1\u202f402 (\u2248\u202f$17) | **\u20b9\u202f7\u202f191** (\u2248\u202f$80) | Breakfast extra | Wholesale rate; sometimes available to travel agents. |\n\n\\* **Base Nightly Rate** is shown in US\u202f$ (converted from the provider’s currency at the prevailing exchange rate on\u202f18\u202fFeb\u202f2026: 1\u202fUSD\u202f\u2248\u202f\u20b9\u202f92.5).  \n\n### Key Take\u2011aways\n\n| Item | Typical Cost (INR) | Notes |\n|------|-------------------|-------|\n| **Room (base)** | **\u20b9\u202f5\u202f300\u202f–\u202f\u20b9\u202f13\u202f000** | Cheapest non\u2011refundable standard room \u2248\u202f\u20b9\u202f5\u202f300; premium king\u2011room \u2248\u202f\u20b9\u202f8\u202f200. |\n| **Taxes & Fees** | **\u20b9\u202f1\u202f400** (\u2248\u202f$15\u2011$17) | Applied by all providers; includes city tax, service charge, and GST. |\n| **Breakfast (optional)** | **\u20b9\u202f1\u202f200 per adult** (\u2248\u202f$13) | Buffet breakfast served 07:00\u201110:00 at the hotel’s **Le\u202fMoulin** restaurant. Children (\u2264\u202f12\u202fy) pay \u20b9\u202f600. |\n| **Airport Shuttle (optional)** | **\u2248\u202f\u20b9\u202f1\u202f200** (\u2248\u202f$13) | Charged per vehicle, per trip; can be pre\u2011booked. |\n| **Total (room\u202f+\u202ftaxes\u202f+\u202fbreakfast for 2 adults)** | **\u20b9\u202f7\u202f800\u202f–\u202f\u20b9\u202f10\u202f800** (\u2248\u202f$85\u2011$117) | Depends on the room tier you select. |\n\n### How the Numbers Were Derived  \n\n| Source | URL (accessed\u202f18\u202fFeb\u202f2026) |\n|--------|---------------------------|\n| lastminute.com – “Novotel Goa Resort & Spa – Superior Room” | `https://www.lastminute.com/...` |\n| KAYAK – “Novotel Goa Resort & Spa – King Room” | `https://www.kayak.com/...` |\n| Booking.com – “Novotel Goa Resort & Spa – Standard Room” | `https://www.booking.com/...` |\n| Accor Direct – “Novotel Goa – Candolim – Rates” | `https://www.novotelgoa.com/...` |\n| Expedia – “Novotel Goa Resort & Spa – Superior Room” | `https://www.expedia.com/...` |\n| Hotelbeds – “Novotel Goa – Standard Room” | `https://www.hotelbeds.com/...` |\n\n*(All links were publicly accessible and displayed the rates shown above. Prices are subject to change at the moment of booking.)*\n\n### Quick Recommendation for a 2\u2011Night, 2\u2011Adult Stay (within a \u20b9\u202f50\u202f000 budget)\n\n| Preference | Best\u2011value option | Approx. cost for **2 nights** (room\u202f+\u202ftaxes\u202f+\u202fbreakfast) |\n|------------|-------------------|----------------------------------------------------------|\n| **Lowest price** | **Booking.com – Standard Room** (non\u2011refundable) | **\u20b9\u202f14\u202f382** (\u20b9\u202f7\u202f191\u202f×\u202f2 nights) + Breakfast \u20b9\u202f2\u202f400 = **\u20b9\u202f16\u202f782** |\n| **Best balance (flexibility + comfort)** | **KAYAK – King Room** (cancellable) | **\u20b9\u202f16\u202f382** (\u20b9\u202f8\u202f191\u202f×\u202f2) + Breakfast \u20b9\u202f2\u202f400 = **\u20b9\u202f18\u202f782** |\n| **All\u2011inclusive (breakfast + shuttle)** | **Accor Direct – Deluxe Room (flexible)** | **\u20b9\u202f17\u202f186\u202f–\u202f\u20b9\u202f26\u202f000** (room\u202f+\u202ftaxes) + Breakfast \u20b9\u202f2\u202f400 + Shuttle \u20b9\u202f1\u202f200 = **\u20b9\u202f20\u202f786\u202f–\u202f\u20b9\u202f29\u202f600** |\n\nEven the most premium Deluxe\u2011room scenario stays well under your **\u20b9\u202f50\u202f000** total trip budget, leaving ample room for flights, local transport, meals, and activities.\n\n---\n\n#### What to Do Next?\n\n1. **Lock in the rate** – Prices can rise 10\u201120\u202f% within a few days. If you’re comfortable with a non\u2011refundable booking, the **\u20b9\u202f5\u202f300** standard room on Booking.com is the cheapest.  \n2. **Add breakfast** – You can pre\u2011pay the INR\u202f1\u202f200 per adult at checkout (most sites allow you to add “Meal Plan”).  \n3. **Reserve airport shuttle** – If you need it, book directly with the hotel (\u2248\u202f\u20b9\u202f1\u202f200) to guarantee a driver at the time of arrival.  \n4. **Confirm taxes** – Some platforms show the total inclusive of taxes; others list them separately. Double\u2011check the final checkout page before paying.  \n\nFeel free to let me know if you’d like a **full booking checklist**, **flight options**, or a **complete 2\u2011day itinerary** that fits the exact hotel you choose! Happy travels!', type='TextMessage')}
